txt.en: 'Very good, [placeholder]! That ought to keep them away from those folk for a bit!'

Nedda Pinleaf has asked you to seek out Harbingers of the Dead among the more treacherous wilds of Middle-earth.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>NOTE: Harbingers of the Dead can be found in the following Skirmishes: Storm on Methedras, Ford of Bruinen, The Icy Crevasse, Attack At Dawn, and Survival: Barrow-downs. You only need to complete four of the five listed quests today to advance this quest.</rgb>

Harbingers of the Dead are assaulting those who dwell in the treacherous wilds of Middle-earth.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>NOTE: This quest will be removed from your quest log when the event it is associated with ends.</rgb>

'[placeholder]!

'I've heard tell that the Harbingers of the Dead have been spotted among the wilder lands of Middle-earth.

'Do what you can, and I'll handle the rest!'
Nedda Pinleaf can be found at the skirmish camps of Bree, Ost Galadh, and the Twenty-first Hall.\n\nYou should talk to Nedda Pinleaf.
<rgb=#8373ff>A Harbinger of the Dead has appeared!</rgb>
